             was indicted for <rs id="t18220417-54-off271" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220417-54-off271" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220417-54-off271" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
